songs.title: Photo
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Gulistan 'ch phull khilan roz
Mere bol sache dost, na milan roz
Jaloos jive mere shows
Mere fan security ton hon na control
Vairi banan nawe dost
Purane yaar banan vairi roz
Jehde samajhdaar sare chup baithe
Jehde jaan de ni mainu ohna nu chaddeya josh
Chamke mere bol, te sitareya 'ch labhan mainu log
Main gehrayi 'ch kinareya 'ch labhan mainu log
Jihna ton mein 7 hazaar meel door rehnda
Ohna sareya ch labhan meinu log
Vairy karan duwa, ve tu aaj girre ga
Raje bas tu kab tak raaj krega?
Par mainu varian di aawaaz ni aundi
Ve noise cancel karan Bose
Assi kadi yaaran ton rakhi ni umeed
Rakho yaad jinha dushmana ne dita saath, ohna nu daat
Nale jehda vi aya maitho lain mera taaj
Kyu hatteya pichhe ve kro yaad
Teri bollyian parchawa, meri bollyian jive raat
Teri bollyian jive chitta, meri bollyian barsaat
Meri bollyian, school di kitaab
Teri bollyian, tu bolleya ki? Kise nu ni yaad
Ve kihnu kihnu haje vi ni yaad aya
Ve pehla main, desi rap mere baad aya
Kihne-kihne mera zehar khaya?
Kihde te chadheya ve mera saya?
Janoon vangu main pehla vangu
Ajay vi vairian di gardna toda, ohna nu sulli tanghu (huh)
Media ch likheya ni par haje vi duniya 'ch koi mere varga ni

[Hook (x2)]
Bachpane 'ch bhajeya nange pairi jehde road te
Ajj uthe photo enni vaddi meri laggi billboard te
Mene akhyian to vekheya jo, loki khawaba 'ch ni soch de
Bachpane 'ch khadi maa di hath di rotti
Ajj hath ch main faddi moti notan di thaddi
Hun mein udh da jahaaza vich
Police labhe mainu road te

Vaddi
Vaddi
Vaddi
Vaddi
Vaddi
Vaddi

Bachpane 'ch bhajeya nange pairi jehde road te

[Verse 2]
Bachpane 'ch bhajeya nange pairi jehde road te
Rok de tok de si jehde kamm to uss hi kamm de karan hun photo laggi meri billboard te
Sochde sochde hun shatranj di chaal
Jehde haar chale pichle modd te
Khed de haje vi naal mere sare vaari vaari
Jehda soch rakhe mere ton jittan di oh anaadi
Vaari vaari munde naal jehde mere ladde
Munde tere naal jinhe chale, nal mere khadde hun
Par tuuuu! Ne haar na manni
Labels da paisa tere te diggeya jive meeh!
Ve industry sarri tere piche ho gayi khadi (yeah)
Par tuuu! Tu mere agge ki ?

[Hook (x2)]
Bachpane 'ch bhajeya nange pairi jehde road te
